### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/api/health

### =====================================
### ORGANIZATIONS
### =====================================

### Get all organizations
GET http://localhost:5000/api/organizations

### Create a new organization
POST http://localhost:5000/api/organizations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New Test Org",
  "email": "test@org.com",
  "phone": "555-5555",
  "address": "123 Main St"
}


### =====================================
### BRANCHES
### =====================================

### Get all branches
GET http://localhost:5000/api/branches

### Create a new branch
POST http://localhost:5000/api/branches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "organization_id": 1,
  "name": "Test Branch Alpha",
  "address": "456 Test Blvd"
}


### =====================================
### FEEDBACK (NEW MVC STRUCTURE)
### =====================================

### Submit Feedback via QR URL (simulate customer scan)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/feedback/submit/QR-X-SUPPORT
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 5,
  "comments": "This new testing file works perfectly!",
  "contactInfo": "tester@test.com"
}

### Get Feedback Reports Data
GET http://localhost:5000/api/feedback/reports


